---
const _ = null;
---

<section class="hero-clibel relative overflow-hidden">
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="hero-blob hero-blob--gold"></div>
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="hero-blob hero-blob--mauve"></div>
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="hero-grain"></div>

  <div class="container-x relative">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <!-- LEFT 50% -->
      <div class="hero-col hero-col--left fade-up">
        <span class="eyebrow-tag">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          Médicos certificados · COFEPRIS · Desde 1981
        </span>

        <h1 class="hero-headline">
          <span class="hero-headline-line">Clínica</span>
          <span class="hero-headline-line">de <em>belleza</em></span>
          <span class="hero-headline-line text-gradient">con criterio médico.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="hero-lede">
          45 años en CDMX. <strong>Medicina estética avanzada</strong> y
          tratamientos diseñados por especialistas, no por catálogo.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-trust">
          <span class="hero-trust-label">Trabajamos con</span>
          <div class="hero-trust-list">
            <span>Allergan</span><span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
            <span>Galderma</span><span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
            <span>Merz</span><span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
            <span>Sculptra</span><span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
            <span>Venus</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT 50% -->
      <div class="hero-col hero-col--right fade-up-delay-2">
        <span class="hero-kicker">Clínica de belleza en Ciudad de México</span>

        <p class="hero-paragraph">
          En <strong>CLIBEL</strong> combinamos medicina estética avanzada,
          tecnología láser de última generación y un equipo de especialistas
          certificados. Ofrecemos tratamientos faciales, corporales, depilación
          láser y terapias capilares con respaldo médico real. Cada protocolo
          se diseña tras una <strong>valoración médica personalizada</strong>,
          sin paquetes prearmados ni presión comercial.
        </p>

        <p class="hero-paragraph">
          <strong>45 años</strong> en CDMX: rejuvenecimiento facial, ácido
          hialurónico, toxina botulínica, plasma rico en plaquetas, hilos
          tensores, radiofrecuencia corporal y peelings químicos — todo en un
          solo lugar, con certificación COFEPRIS y marcas internacionales.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-clibel {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-brand-50) 0%, var(--color-brand-100) 100%);
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(60% 50% at 80% 0%, rgba(201,169,97,0.18), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(50% 50% at 0% 100%, rgba(139,90,107,0.16), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .hero-blob {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 999px;
    filter: blur(110px);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: .5;
  }
  .hero-blob--gold {
    width: 36rem; height: 36rem;
    top: -10rem; right: -10rem;
    background: var(--color-brand-300);
  }
  .hero-blob--mauve {
    width: 32rem; height: 32rem;
    bottom: -12rem; left: -8rem;
    background: var(--color-mauve-300);
  }
  .hero-grain {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(31,20,24,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 3px 3px;
    opacity: .35;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* ===== Grid 50 / 50 ===== */
  .hero-grid {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid !important;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    padding-block: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
    width: 100% !important;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr !important;
      gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4.5rem);
    }
  }

  .hero-col {
    min-width: 0 !important;
    width: 100% !important;
    max-width: 100% !important;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }

  /* ===== LEFT ===== */
  .hero-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 0.92;
    color: var(--color-ink-900);
    font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 7vw, 7rem);
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .hero-headline-line {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .hero-headline em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-mauve-500);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .hero-lede {
    font-size: clamp(0.98rem, 1.05vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-ink-700);
    margin: 0;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .hero-lede strong { color: var(--color-ink-900); font-weight: 600; }

  .hero-trust {
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.25);
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: 0.85rem;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .hero-trust-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-mauve-500);
  }
  .hero-trust-list {
    display: inline-flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.55rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-700);
  }
  .hero-trust-list span[aria-hidden] { color: var(--color-brand-400); }

  /* ===== RIGHT ===== */
  .hero-col--right { gap: 1.25rem; }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .hero-col--right {
      padding-left: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2.5rem);
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.25);
    }
  }

  .hero-kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-mauve-500);
    padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-brand-400);
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .hero-paragraph {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1vw, 1.05rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-ink-700);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .hero-paragraph strong {
    color: var(--color-ink-900);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 899px) {
    .hero-col { gap: 1.25rem; }
  }
</style>
